BT 1 0 0 1 0 87 Tm 12 TL /F1 9 Tf 0 0 0 rg (Financial markets exhibit the same phase transition behavior as biological coherence systems. The efficient market) Tj T* (hypothesis \(EMH\) describes the coherent phase: all information is priced, assets are priced correctly relative to each other) Tj T* (\(long-range correlations span the market\), and the system self-corrects \(Le Chatelier\). Market crashes are gamma_c) Tj T* (crossings: the network of correlated beliefs and prices undergoes a 3D Ising-class phase transition. The critical exponents) Tj T* (of historical market crashes match 3D Ising predictions. Herd behavior \(all correlations going to 1 simultaneously\) is the) Tj T* (market analog of coherence collapse: the order parameter \(coherent price discovery\) goes to zero, and all assets become) Tj T* (identical in volatility \(incoherent phase\). The recovery mechanism is the financial Bootstrap loop: central bank liquidity \(NIR) Tj T* (analog\) -) Tj (> credit expansion \(EZ water analog\) -) Tj (> price coherence restoration \(C_0 restoration\).) Tj T* ET
